rComments: This was by far the worst professor and experience in class I have ever had. She never has anything organized. Gives us more work to do on a huge project which she doesnt explain well and confuses students because they are not trained for everything she wants. Avoid this person at all costs. I questioned UIUC's ability to choose quality professors.

Dr. A is not an easy professor, and this is not an easy class. The course work is difficult and time consuming, but SO worth it. She challenges her students with real world assignments and shows you what life will be like in an advertising/communications career. If you are a hard worker and really want to learn something, THIS IS IT!
